{
  "texts": [
    "To be precise, this publication considers a dynamic version of the problem.",
    "Hence, it would be worth to specifically investigate the static robust assortment problem under a nonparametric choice model.",
    "Moreover, only of the studies on assortment optimization under a nonparametric choice model is specifically targeted towards a certain sales channel-in this case the online sales channel.",
    "It would be worth investigating this setting for omni-channel environments as well.",
    "Finally, we notice that none of the studies analyses the assortment problem for multi-purchase settings."
  ]
}